    <p>The website is fully open-source, and contributions are welcome! Get involved by forking the <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-website">openjdk-website repository</a> on GitHub.</p>
    <p>The <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/AdoptOpenJDK/openjdk-website/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md">Contributing Guide</a> is regularly updated, and should help to get you up and running.</p>
